    <section name="Binary Distributions">
      
      <p>
      Current binary distributions of the DPML products are available from the 
      <a href="http://www.osm.net/download/index.html">OSM Download Center</a>.
      Unlike earlier versions we are moving towatards the centralization of 
      product installation and configuration via the Depot Application Management
      tool.  The upcomming release of Depot will provide convinient, automatic, 
      and reliable installation of all DPML products.
      </p>

      <p><i>Stay tunned for product announcements ...</i></p>

    </section>

